@startuml program-lifecycle
title Program Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Created by Vertical Owner

Draft --> Requested : Submitted for Review
Requested --> Reviewed : Peer / Expert Review Complete
Reviewed --> Approved : Umbrella Admin signs off

Approved --> Active : Reaches ActiveFrom date
Active --> Restricted : Policy Audit / Emergency Freeze
Active --> Suspended : Violation detected

Active --> Deprecated : Program Replaced by New Version
Deprecated --> Archived : Historical Reference (Read-Only)

@enduml
